    "description": "<strong>欢迎来到 Alpha Rooms！</strong><br><br>用你的智慧穿越这个充满陷阱的世界。每一个错误的决定都可能导致死亡。预见危险并制定策略将成为你最强大的武器。你能在不失去现实感的情况下挑战这片无尽的世界吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014230/extras/3abf48abd493c612e270869055ebd7e1.avif?t=1725947116\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><strong>探索未知的深渊</strong><br><br>踏入 Alpha Rooms 的未知深渊。每个房间都隐藏着一个故事和等待解开的谜团。在追寻苏联秘密的过程中，跟随美国探险家留下的线索。但要小心，每一步都会让你深入未知。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014230/extras/eabd9404506092c74ccca808604729d9.poster.avif?t=1725947116\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014230/extras/eabd9404506092c74ccca808604729d9.webm?t=1725947116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014230/extras/eabd9404506092c74ccca808604729d9.mp4?t=1725947116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>无处可逃，勇敢面对！</strong><br><br>Alpha Rooms 的每个角落都有敌人埋伏。要想生存，你必须逃跑、躲藏并运用策略。直接面对敌人并非总是最佳选择，因为等待你的不仅仅是身体上的威胁，还有心灵的考验。选择逃跑吧，否则时间将成为你的敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014230/extras/f19a38839b6d320925e7b11490099f01.poster.avif?t=1725947116\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014230/extras/f19a38839b6d320925e7b11490099f01.webm?t=1725947116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014230/extras/f19a38839b6d320925e7b11490099f01.mp4?t=1725947116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>无尽迷宫：迷失的心灵</strong><br><br>在这个没有起点和终点的迷宫中，你将挑战现实的极限。每一步都会让你陷得更深，但每个拐角可能都是死胡同。当你听到迷失心灵的低语时，你将意识到已经无法回头。你能找到出口吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014230/extras/7cd0d58dc323d5d4d509a7dd38793cfb.poster.avif?t=1725947116\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014230/extras/7cd0d58dc323d5d4d509a7dd38793cfb.webm?t=1725947116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014230/extras/7cd0d58dc323d5d4d509a7dd38793cfb.mp4?t=1725947116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>现实扭曲的瞬间</strong><br><br>Alpha Rooms 独特的氛围扭曲了现实，将你拉入一个令人不安的世界。每一刻你都会质疑什么是真实的；真相与幻觉之间的界限会逐渐模糊。在这个世界中，只有勇敢者才能发现真相，其他人则会迷失。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014230/extras/21c614c393b9815db36452cfed92fcc5.poster.avif?t=1725947116\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014230/extras/21c614c393b9815db36452cfed92fcc5.webm?t=1725947116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014230/extras/21c614c393b9815db36452cfed92fcc5.mp4?t=1725947116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
